Daphne!

06:09.952 --> 06:11.953
I don't understand.

06:12.021 --> 06:14.756
How can this have happened?
My trap, Daphne...

06:14.823 --> 06:17.592
I'm so confused!

06:17.660 --> 06:20.094
Why?!

06:23.122 --> 06:26.124
All right. Now, let me
get this straight.

06:26.192 --> 06:29.361
These t-shirts are $50 each.

06:29.428 --> 06:32.964
This is cotton, right?
The kind that comes from cows?

06:33.032 --> 06:34.332
Sheriff, focus.

06:34.400 --> 06:36.334
The phantom has taken Daphne.

06:36.402 --> 06:38.503
Right. Any suspects?

06:38.571 --> 06:39.738
The phantom!

06:39.805 --> 06:42.474
All right!
Now we're gettin' somewhere.

06:42.542 --> 06:45.343
By the way, what's wrong
with the Jones kid?

06:45.411 --> 06:47.913
He's acting a little...

06:47.980 --> 06:49.915
Squirrelly.

06:49.982 --> 06:52.851
I'm sorry, gang. I've just
got all these crazy emotions,

06:52.919 --> 06:56.221
and I don't know why.
Am I upset over my trap not working?

06:56.289 --> 06:58.256
Or is it because Daphne's gone?

06:58.324 --> 07:01.159
Why can't I just be cold and
heartless like other guys?

07:01.227 --> 07:04.429
Why must I feel? 
It's ok, Fred.

07:04.497 --> 07:06.164
♪ Freddy ♪

07:06.232 --> 07:08.833
♪ you're a special boy ♪

07:08.901 --> 07:11.002
So, what's our next move,
sheriff?

07:11.070 --> 07:12.804
Heh! Don't look at me.

07:12.872 --> 07:15.540
An unsanctioned class 4
non-corporeal phantom

07:15.608 --> 07:18.043
stalking a public
musical performance arena?

07:18.110 --> 07:19.811
Where do ya even start?

07:19.879 --> 07:21.713
So, you're just gonna
do nothing?

07:21.781 --> 07:23.481
Uh, absolutely not.
For starters,

07:23.549 --> 07:25.417
I'm gonna take a couple of
these Hex Girl t-shirts

07:25.484 --> 07:28.620
so I didn't waste a trip down here,
and then I'm gonna call the Mayor.

07:28.688 --> 07:31.990
'Cause that's what I do.

07:32.058 --> 07:33.592
Well, gang,

07:33.659 --> 07:36.361
looks like it's up to us
to solve this mystery.

07:41.033 --> 07:42.267
Oh.

07:42.335 --> 07:43.835
Gotcha.

07:45.137 --> 07:46.905
Ooh.

07:46.973 --> 07:48.006
Oh.

07:48.074 --> 07:49.608
Like, go ahead, Scooby-Doo.

07:49.675 --> 07:51.509
It's all yours.

07:51.577 --> 07:53.245
Ruff.

07:53.312 --> 07:54.779
Oh, come on, Scoob.

07:54.847 --> 07:56.681
Like, you got to talk to me
at some point, dude.

07:56.749 --> 07:59.851
If you don't, we're gonna have
to find new best friends, right?

07:59.919 --> 08:01.519
Good idea.

08:01.587 --> 08:03.888
Like, what's a good idea?
Scoob?

08:03.956 --> 08:05.757
Buddy? Aah!

08:05.825 --> 08:08.627
Get a hold of yourself, Fred.
Be a man.

08:08.694 --> 08:10.629
Keep repeating.
You're dead inside.

08:10.696 --> 08:12.397
You're dead inside.

08:12.465 --> 08:15.800
Wait a sec. Why is there
lotion on these ropes?

08:15.868 --> 08:19.337
I don't moisturize.
This can only mean one thing...

08:19.405 --> 08:23.508
sabotage! The trap malfunction
wasn't my fault!

08:25.678 --> 08:28.546
So, why do I still feel lousy?

08:28.614 --> 08:30.148
Daphne. Uhh.

08:30.216 --> 08:32.049
I wish I didn't care about her.

08:37.356 --> 08:38.789
Freddy!

08:38.857 --> 08:42.594
I do. I care about Daphne!

08:42.662 --> 08:44.496
Gang...

08:44.563 --> 08:47.132
I've had a breakthrough! Dad?

08:47.199 --> 08:49.734
What are you doing here?
My job as Mayor...

08:49.802 --> 08:51.403
or, at least,
what I interpret that to be.

08:51.470 --> 08:54.139
Mayor handsome here just moved
tomorrow night's happening

08:54.206 --> 08:56.107
to terror dome stadium.

08:56.175 --> 08:58.677
Let loose the doves of change!

08:58.744 --> 09:01.212
I've also declared tomorrow
phantom day.

09:01.280 --> 09:03.281
So, leave the phantom
alone, Fred.

09:03.349 --> 09:06.518
He's good for business.
But you don't understand.

09:06.585 --> 09:09.321
Someone sabotaged my trap.
And Daphne...

09:09.388 --> 09:10.989
is right here.

09:11.057 --> 09:13.224
Daphne!

09:13.292 --> 09:14.526
- Oh!
- Hey!

09:14.593 --> 09:16.061
- Hey.
- Daphne.

09:16.128 --> 09:18.229
And I heard every word, Fred.

09:18.297 --> 09:20.565
Wish you didn't care
for Daphne, huh?

09:20.633 --> 09:23.034
Wait, Daphne. You didn't hear
the whole thing.

09:23.102 --> 09:24.736
Save it
for your traps.

09:24.804 --> 09:26.638
I think this proves
it's too dangerous

09:26.706 --> 09:28.506
for anyone to go
on stage tomorrow night.

09:28.574 --> 09:30.508
It's time to cancel the tour.

09:30.576 --> 09:32.510
Wrong.
I'm going on tomorrow.

09:32.578 --> 09:34.079
And I'm gonna rock!

09:38.951 --> 09:42.020
Perfect. Glad we're all
on the same page.

09:43.889 --> 09:47.158
Wow. Could this get
any weirder?

09:47.226 --> 09:50.528
Like, scoob, what are you
doing with my dummy?

09:50.596 --> 09:53.898
What are you talking about?
This is my new best friend...

09:53.966 --> 09:55.333
Harry.

09:55.401 --> 09:58.536
Hi. I'm Harry.
I love food.

09:58.604 --> 10:01.740
And I'll never leave Scooby
for a girl.

10:02.708 --> 10:04.876
He's so your dog.

10:04.944 --> 10:08.613
Sorry, shag.
I got my own problems.

10:10.182 --> 10:12.016
Like, oh, boy.

10:15.054 --> 10:16.988
Make me a rock star.

10:17.056 --> 10:18.890
- Are you sure you want to...
- Do it!

10:30.803 --> 10:33.838
Could you make me
a rock star, too?

10:35.341 --> 10:38.143
Or I could just do it myself.
Good idea.

10:52.992 --> 10:56.327
I'm tired of being afraid.
I have feelings, world,

10:56.395 --> 10:58.630
for traps and Daphne!

10:58.697 --> 11:01.166
I'm a guy no more.

11:01.233 --> 11:04.102
I'm coming, Daphne!

11:09.875 --> 11:11.776
Daphne. Now.

11:11.844 --> 11:13.945
I need to talk to her.

11:14.013 --> 11:15.947
Daphne's gone.

11:17.450 --> 11:19.250
Call me crush.

11:19.318 --> 11:21.519
Darn it, lady, I'm serious.
Where is she?

11:21.587 --> 11:23.955
Uhh. Fred, it's me. Ok?

11:24.023 --> 11:26.424
Uh, oh.

11:26.492 --> 11:28.993
I need to tell you something,
and I need you to listen.

11:29.061 --> 11:31.663
I'm not a guy anymore.
What?!

11:31.730 --> 11:34.532
I have feelings! I care!

11:34.600 --> 11:37.202
Don't you see?
Uh, no.

11:37.269 --> 11:39.671
You can't go on
tomorrow night. It's too risky.

11:39.738 --> 11:42.173
Don't tell me what to do,
Fred. I can go on.

11:42.241 --> 11:44.175
And I will. Ladies?

11:46.111 --> 11:48.413
- But Daphne...
- It's crush.

11:48.481 --> 11:51.082
Bad dreams, Fred.

11:51.150 --> 11:53.985
Huh?

11:54.053 --> 11:56.654
That's the first time you
stood up for yourself with Fred,

11:56.722 --> 11:57.856
ever.

11:57.923 --> 12:00.391
Are you ok?
Truth?

12:00.459 --> 12:01.726
No.

12:03.796 --> 12:05.463
But I care about you.

12:05.531 --> 12:08.766
You wouldn't if you knew
what was lurking inside me.

12:08.834 --> 12:11.836
It wouldn't matter.
I'd still love you.

12:11.904 --> 12:13.104
Even...

12:13.172 --> 12:14.506
With a lizard face?

12:14.573 --> 12:16.608
Aah! You're right!

12:16.675 --> 12:18.610
Run away! Run away!

12:20.846 --> 12:22.881
If you had a lizard face,

12:22.948 --> 12:25.316
I'd still love you, Scooby.

12:25.384 --> 12:27.452
And I'd love you, Harry.

12:27.520 --> 12:30.255
More sandwich?

12:30.322 --> 12:32.524
Ok. Like, you know what?
Enough.

12:32.591 --> 12:34.726
You can't replace me
with a dummy.

12:34.793 --> 12:37.395
Do you hear something, Harry?

12:37.463 --> 12:39.797
There is no Harry.
Harry is you.

12:39.865 --> 12:42.500
And, like, dude,
I am your best friend.

12:42.568 --> 12:44.903
Um, no. I don't think so.

12:44.970 --> 12:47.205
Why don't you just
stay out of it, Harry?

12:47.273 --> 12:49.841
And, like, stop watching
Vincent van Ghoul movies.

12:49.909 --> 12:52.076
That's mine
and Scooby-Doo's thing.

12:52.144 --> 12:54.145
Really?
Well, Scooby thought

12:54.213 --> 12:57.048
you cared more about girls
and going to proms.

13:00.052 --> 13:02.220
Get him, Harry.

13:04.957 --> 13:07.859
Wait. What am I doing?
You're just a puppet!

13:07.927 --> 13:10.261
You can't fight back, puppet!

13:10.329 --> 13:12.297
Uhh, uhh, uhh!

13:14.967 --> 13:18.403
What is this
on the floor I see?

13:18.470 --> 13:20.338
One head or 3?

13:20.406 --> 13:22.874
Soon dead they'll be.

13:22.942 --> 13:25.777
It's... it's... it's...

13:25.844 --> 13:28.012
The phantom!

13:32.898 --> 13:34.498
Run, Harry!

13:34.566 --> 13:36.233
- H-harry?

13:52.684 --> 13:54.351
Scoob.

14:04.596 --> 14:07.598
We should, like, check to see
if he's gone.

14:07.666 --> 14:10.034
- Uh-uh. Not me.
Not gonna do it.

14:10.101 --> 14:12.102
Well, I'm not gonna do it,
either.

14:14.439 --> 14:17.842
Hmm. Something's burning.

14:17.909 --> 14:19.510
Huh?
Huh?

14:19.578 --> 14:21.178
Yeah. Us!

14:21.246 --> 14:23.581
Yikes!

14:23.648 --> 14:25.349
Like, we're trapped!

14:25.417 --> 14:28.085
Help, Harry! Save us!

14:28.153 --> 14:30.554
Hey! Good thinking, scoob!

14:30.622 --> 14:32.323
Unh!

14:34.559 --> 14:36.827
Oh.

14:40.732 --> 14:44.268
Aw, you saved me.

14:44.336 --> 14:46.904
Like, it's no big deal.

14:46.972 --> 14:49.073
Thank you, Harry.

14:49.140 --> 14:51.709
Harry?! What about me?

14:51.776 --> 14:53.878
Hey. What's this?

14:53.945 --> 14:56.514
It's a piece of
the phantom's robe. Huh.

14:56.581 --> 14:59.450
Dude, I think I've seen
this material before.

14:59.518 --> 15:02.820
- ♪ Dance in my pants, dance
in my pants ♪ - ♪ Hey! ♪

15:02.888 --> 15:05.289
