15:12.864 --> 15:14.798
His pants match.

15:14.866 --> 15:16.967
And look. Fantzee Pantz
had the same manager

15:17.035 --> 15:19.670
as the Hex Girls...
Gus Boggs.

15:19.738 --> 15:21.272
Boggs could be the phantom.

15:21.339 --> 15:23.007
Harry, get him again.

15:23.074 --> 15:26.043
Aw, come on, scoob!

15:28.413 --> 15:29.847
♪ When the demon chants ♪

15:29.915 --> 15:32.416
♪ dance in my pants,
dance in my pants ♪

15:35.387 --> 15:37.688
Pray think I'm the phantom

15:37.756 --> 15:40.491
because I was
fantzee Pantz's manager?

15:40.559 --> 15:43.027
Heh heh heh. Groovy chiclets.

15:43.094 --> 15:45.429
Fantzee Pantz
went down the rabbit hole

15:45.497 --> 15:47.831
after the record gods
dumped him

15:47.899 --> 15:50.434
to make room for the Hex Girls.

15:50.502 --> 15:54.638
Poor fantzee.
We knew him well.

15:54.706 --> 15:56.407
What do we do now, Fred?

15:56.474 --> 15:58.542
I'm sure Harry will save us.

15:58.610 --> 16:00.611
Harry is not saving...

16:00.679 --> 16:04.214
hold on, Shaggy. Maybe Harry
is exactly what we need.

16:12.624 --> 16:14.058
Stop. Stop!

16:14.125 --> 16:16.226
It still doesn't feel right.

16:17.562 --> 16:20.331
Luna, dusk,
why don't you take five?

16:20.398 --> 16:23.200
I'm sorry, Thorn.
I know you were counting on me.

16:23.268 --> 16:26.070
That's ok.
I know what's going on.

16:26.137 --> 16:28.172
We've all had a Fred
in our lives.

16:28.239 --> 16:31.842
Mine was a carny I met on the
road named knuckles Wazinski.

16:31.910 --> 16:34.878
He ran the roundup.
You know that ride that spins around,

16:34.946 --> 16:37.281
pinning you to the wall
till you puke?

16:37.349 --> 16:39.116
Loved it more than me.

16:39.184 --> 16:41.552
Last time I saw knuckles,
he was going 60 miles an hour

16:41.620 --> 16:44.388
covered in a 4-year-old's
chili cheese fries.

16:44.456 --> 16:47.157
You know how I got over him?
You cut the brake lines on his van.

16:47.225 --> 16:49.727
No. I got over it
with a song.

16:49.794 --> 16:52.563
Now, why don't we sit down
and write one?

